  <ProductSchemaDescription>
    <![CDATA[<p>Durable neoprene-padded collar with 360° reflective stitching for safer walks day or night.</p><p>Built for everyday walks and weekend adventures, the TrailFlex collar combines a tough nylon webbing core with soft neoprene padding to reduce rubbing. Reflective stitching improves visibility in low light, and a rust-resistant D-ring keeps your leash and tags secure. Easy to clean, quick to dry.</p>]]>
